programme.desc: Tim Herald returns to Africa to hunt in Uganda. Across the world, Mark Peterson is hunting in Kentucky alongside a special guest: his daughter(n)

programme.title: Small Town Hunting
programme.sub-title: Small Town Wexford Way Part II
programme.desc: Part 2. Hoyts, Bergara rifles and big bucks at the Wexford Ranch. Everyone ends the season on a really good note(n)

programme.title: Country Boys Outdoors
programme.desc: It's a bucket list kind of hunt for Brad Miller as we find the gang in the deep forest of Denali trying to get a bull moose down with a bow. Unfortunately with bad weather and muddy terrain, this might prove a little tricky(n)

programme.title: Major League Bowhunter
programme.desc: Brandon Danker has a giant within range during late season in Kansas. After filming and taking the largest deer of his life the previous year, Brandon has his sights set on yet another giant on the same farm(n)

programme.title: Brotherhood Outdoors
programme.desc: Travis Simmons is a dedicated member of the International Union of Operating Engineers and Local 673 in his home state of Florida. An avid outdoorsman since childhood, Travis shares his excitement when he embarks on a memorable fly-fishing trip(n)

programme.title: Extreme Outer Limits TV
programme.desc: Part 2. Bob Beck and the crew find a giant Oregon bull in the bottom of the ninth(n)

programme.title: Guns & Gear
programme.desc: A look at DoubleTap Ammunition's newest ammo loaded with Swift Scirocco bullets. Also: hearing protection from Walker's; Colt's Combat Unit carbine; SureFire's MasterFire holster system; the family of Ruger American pistols; and more(n)

programme.title: Guns & Ammo TV
programme.desc: Ruger has quickly moved to the forefront in suppressed rimfires with threaded barrel .22 firearms, its very own .22 suppressor and an integrated suppressed 10/22. Nikon has its first-ever laser rangefinger/binocular package(n)

programme.title: West of Texas
programme.desc: After fellow outfitter and partner Brad Peacock tells Stephen about a trophy mule deer he has spotted, the hunt is on for a buck named Stetson. These two friends brave the elements and learn some tough lessons along the way(n)

programme.title: Sheep Shape
programme.desc: Chad Hall takes on the frozen arctic in search of a mature muskox. Chad's friend, David, closes the distance on a muskox with his bow(n)

programme.title: Fresh Tracks With Randy Newberg
programme.desc: Tim Lesser joins Randy Newberg for another week, but this time they are chasing New Mexico elk in a large wilderness burn. Getting to them and packing one out are huge challenges(n)

programme.title: Long Range Pursuit
programme.desc: The story of Clint West and his 2015 Utah elk hunt(n)

programme.title: Into High Country
programme.desc: Jason hunts his home state of Montana in pursuit of black bear deep in the rugged mountains. After hunting all spring, Jason goes home empty-handed, but not from lack of trying(n)

programme.title: The Western Hunter
programme.desc: Nate and Randy return to one of their favorite elk hunting honeyholes in Idaho's backcountry. Nate regrets not having a deer tag and ends up alone, which makes filming a spot-and-stalk elk hunt a little tricky(n)

programme.title: Wild Outdoors
programme.desc: Jake Latendresse has a documentary series called The Other Side. This is a highlight of Jay Gregory's other side and a horrific incident he had in the early 90's(n)

programme.title: The Lindsey Way
programme.desc: Jeff and Ashley Lindsey are in the blind for Iowa late season and a familiar buck shows up for the food. After skirting Ashley, Jeff rolls the dice the next evening . He made the right choice, but bad luck wasn't far behind(n)

programme.title: Big Deer TV *
programme.desc: From the deserts of Oregon to the swamps of Florida, Mike crisscrosses the country in search of the biggest, baddest hunting rigs. He discovers an eccentric and dedicated group of hunters, guides and gearheads who take their wheels seriously(n)

programme.title: Bowlife
programme.desc: It's early October and the entire Morgan family is hunting the family farm in Ohio. While Levi is busy figuring out a giant nine-point, his dad is wasting no time punching his first tag(n)
